These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, cola
There 3 different types of food: pear, strawberry, pumpkin
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, teacher, writer
1. the chef is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the writer##1
3. the person drinking water is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating pumpkin##2
4. the chef is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the fan of trance is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage         | 7up | water   | cola   |
| Food   | strawberry     | pear | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Job     | teacher     | chef      | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, palace
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, rugby
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, june, may
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the craftsman house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the palace house##2
6. the palace house is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| House          | craftsman  | gothic-revival     | palace     |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | rugby     | weightlifting      |
| Birthday   | may  | june | july |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, mexican
House: wooden, victorian, gothic-revival
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, emerald, pink
1. the nigerian is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person who likes amber is between the mexican and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes emerald is the person eating kale##1
5. the person who likes amber is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Nationality           | mexican | nigerian  | canadian   |
| House   | wooden  | victorian    | gothic-revival |
| Color           | pink     | amber | emerald |

