.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
House: wooden, cottage, victorian
City: prague, miami, san-francisco
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, tulip
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the cottage house and the person traveling to prague##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| House     | cottage    | victorian  | wooden |
| City     | miami   | san-francisco | prague        |
| Flower   | tulip | zinnia     | sunflower      |

