.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, trike
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, bridge
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
House: wooden, palace, ranch-style
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the wooden house is between the fan of gospel and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the palace house##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Transport          | trike    | jet-ski     | boat      |
| Game         | mah-jongg | go | bridge |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| House           | palace     | wooden       | ranch-style     |

