.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, april
3 different games are played: billiard, canasta, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, bike, airplane
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person who's birthday is in october and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | october | january | april    |
| Game         | canasta | whist      | billiard |
| Transport   | bus   | bike     | airplane        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

