.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop, soul
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, analyst, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the analyst is between the fan of soul and the person who growsrose##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
5. the analyst is between the scientist and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | soul      | hip-hop   | reggae |
| Job         | pilot | analyst | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Flower     | daffodil         | tulip  | rose       |

