3 different games are played: poker, snooker, bridge
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, green, lavender
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, ambient, blues
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person playing snooker is between the person playing poker and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who likes green is the person playing bridge##1
5. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing poker##1
6. the fan of punk is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Game         | bridge | snooker | poker |
| Color       | green      | lavender         | lilac |
| Music-Genre   | punk        | blues            | ambient  |

