3. the swisher-smoker is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes orange##2
4. the old-henry-smoker is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who growspoppy and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | marigold | lily     | poppy        |
| Color         | purple   | lilac | orange |
| Cigar   | old-henry        | swisher       | siglo      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

