.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, chinese, canadian
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, sunflower
City: berlin, nizza, prague
1. the french is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person who growszinnia is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person who growsorchid is the canadian##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person traveling to prague and the person who growszinnia##2
6. the person who growssunflower is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality        | chinese      | french | canadian |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Flower       | zinnia | sunflower   | orchid   |
| City   | berlin          | nizza     | prague       |

 